<abstract>
<p>In the book review published in <italic>Journal of Classical Sociology</italic> 13(1), pp. 108–112, DOI: <related-article ext-link-type="doi" id="related-article2-1468795X13488288" issue="1" page="108" related-article-type="corrected-article" vol="13" xlink:href="10.1177/1468795X12461701">10.1177/1468795X12461701</related-article>, an error has been identified:</p>
</abstract>
