<body>
<p>On page 108, in the book review information, the introduction was authored by Daniel Silver and Donald N. Levine, and not by John A.Y. Andrews.</p>
<p>The correct information is as follows:</p>
<p>Georg Simmel</p>
<p><italic>The View of Life: Four Metaphysical Essays with Journal Aphorisms</italic>, trans. John A.Y. Andrews and Donald N. Levine; Introduction by Daniel Silver and Donald N. Levine. Chicago: University of Chicago Press, 2010. 240 pp. ISBN 978-0-2267-5783-4 (hbk).</p>
<p><bold>Reviewed by:</bold> Thomas Cushman, Wellesley College, USA</p>
